            Our Services & Initiatives
          Heading link



 
Copy link












                            Recruitment & Admission Assistance
                    

                Recruiters guide students through the application process and promote interest in higher education and college readiness
            












                            Advising & Student Development
                    

                This provides a comprehensive plan of services and programs to assist with the retention, persistence, and graduation.
            











